"title": "8237: doctrine, false",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "8237: doctrine, false",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>Teaching that distorts or contradicts the revealed truth of God, causing division and distress in the church by leading people away from the truth.</p>\n<h2>False doctrine deviates from the truth</h2>\n<h3>It contradicts the gospel of Jesus Christ</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jude1:3-Jude1:4\">JUD 1:3–1:4</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor3:10-1Cor3:13\">1CO 3:10–3:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor11:3-2Cor11:4\">2CO 11:3–11:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal1:6-Gal1:7\">GAL 1:6–1:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim6:3-1Tim6:4\">1TI 6:3–6:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2John1:7\">2JN 1:7</a></p>\n<h3>It may be of human origin</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col2:8\">COL 2:8</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col2:20-Col2:23\">COL 2:20–2:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt15:8-Matt15:9\">MAT 15:8–15:9</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark7:6-Mark7:7\">MRK 7:6–7:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa29:13\">ISA 29:13</a></p>\n<h2>It may be of demonic origin</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim4:1-1Tim4:5\">1TI 4:1–4:5</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John4:2-1John4:3\">1JN 4:2–4:3</a></p>\n<h2>The dangers of false doctrine</h2>\n<h3>It leads to instability and confusion</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph4:14\">EPH 4:14</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts15:24\">ACT 15:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal1:7\">GAL 1:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim1:18-1Tim1:20\">1TI 1:18–1:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim2:16-2Tim2:18\">2TI 2:16–2:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Titus1:10-Titus1:11\">TIT 1:10–1:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb13:9\">HEB 13:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Pet3:17\">2PE 3:17</a></p>\n<h3>It causes division</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom16:17-Rom16:18\">ROM 16:17–16:18</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim1:3-1Tim1:4\">1TI 1:3–1:4</a></p>\n<h3>It leads to severe punishment</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal1:8-Gal1:9\">GAL 1:8–1:9</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor11:13-2Cor11:15\">2CO 11:13–11:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Pet2:1\">2PE 2:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Pet2:17\">2PE 2:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev2:14-Rev2:16\">REV 2:14–2:16</a></p>\n<h2>False doctrine is to be dealt with by the church</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Titus1:10-Titus1:11\">TIT 1:10–1:11</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim1:3\">1TI 1:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Titus1:13-Titus1:14\">TIT 1:13–1:14</a></p>\n<h2>False doctrine will be common in later times</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim4:1\">1TI 4:1</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark13:5-Mark13:6\">MRK 13:5–13:6</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke21:8\">LUK 21:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Thess2:3\">2TH 2:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim4:3-2Tim4:4\">2TI 4:3–4:4</a></p>",
